'''蓮花菰'''（學名：''{{lang|la|Thonningia sanguinea}}''）是屬於[[蛇菰科|蛇菰科]]'''蓮花菰屬'''的一種[[寄生植物|寄生植物]]，蓮花菰屬是一個[[單種屬|單種屬]]，屬內只有蓮花菰一個種。<ref name=siu>Nickrent, D. [http://www.parasiticplants.siu.edu/ListParasites.html#anchor423964 Parasitic Plant Classification.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.parasiticplants.siu.edu/ListParasites.html#anchor423964 |date=20200103223941 }} The Parasitic Plant Connection. Department of Plant Biology, Southern Illinois University, Carbondale.</ref><ref name=lei>Leistner, O. A. (2005). [http://www.sabonet.org.za/downloads/26_seedplants/b_seeds_pages55-109.pdf Balanophoraceae.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081121052044/http://www.sabonet.org.za/downloads/26_seedplants/b_seeds_pages55-109.pdf |date=2008-11-21 }} ''Seed Plants of Southern Tropical Africa: Families and Genera''. Southern African Botanical Diversity Network Report No. 26. pg 103.</ref>分布遍及[[非洲|非洲]]南部和西部，尤其是非洲的熱帶地區特別多。<ref name=lei/><ref name=sei>{{cite book |first=Johannes |last=Seidemann |chapter=Thonningia Vahl – Balanophoraceae |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=fhN0VK2608QC&pg=PA364 |page=364 |title=World Spice Plants: Economic Usage, Botany, Taxonomy |publisher=Springer |year=2005 |isbn=978-3-540-22279-8 |access-date=2014-10-13 |archive-date=2014-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704182426/http://books.google.com/books?id=fhN0VK2608QC&pg=PA364 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

蓮花菰，俗稱'''地鳳梨'''（ground pineapple），<ref name=sei/><ref name=burk>Burkill, H. M. (1985). [http://plants.jstor.org/upwta/1_523 ''Thonningia sanguinea''.] ''The Useful Plants of West Tropical Africa, Vol 1.'' Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew.</ref>是一種非洲人非常熟悉的植物，在非洲的眾多語言中它有著一長串各種不同的俗名，因為[[花序|花序]]的外觀像小型的[[鳳梨|鳳梨]]或[[棕櫚科|椰子樹]]，這些俗名大多和鳳梨或是椰子樹有關。<ref name=neu>{{cite book |first=Hans Dieter |last=Neuwinger |year=1996 |chapter=Thonningia sanguinea Vahl |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=_j8ueEmakD0C&pg=PA249 |pages=249–51 |title=African Ethnobotany: Poisons and Drugs; Chemistry, Pharmacology, Toxicology |publisher=CRC Press |isbn=978-3-8261-0077-2 |access-date=2014-10-13 |archive-date=2014-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704182527/http://books.google.com/books?id=_j8ueEmakD0C&pg=PA249 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 形態特徵 ==
本種是雌雄異株的肉質[[草本植物|草本植物]]，[[塊莖|塊莖]]生長在地底下，經由塊莖寄生在宿主植物上。淺黃色的塊莖生長在土壤中，會由塊莖長出分枝，分枝水平延伸約10〜15公分長，在接觸宿主植物根的地方會形成腫脹的[[癭|癭瘤]]，這些癭瘤可以成長到18公分寬。<ref name=oto>{{cite journal |doi=10.1080/09670878209370698|title=Thonningia sanguinea— a new parasite on rubber roots|journal=Tropical Pest Management|volume=28|issue=2|pages=186|year=1982|last1=Otoide|first1=V. O.}}</ref>
塊莖看起來很像是[[根莖|根狀莖]]，但它們並不是真正的根狀莖。莖上覆蓋著鱗片狀的葉片，鱗葉呈螺旋狀排列。葉子顏色不是綠色的，沒有[[葉綠素|葉綠素]]，因為養分是取自宿主植物，本身不需要進行[[光合作用|光合作用]]製造養分。花莖直接由地底的塊莖長出，皇冠狀的花頭覆蓋著鱗片，[[花序|花序]]鮮紅色或粉紅色，花單性，花序長15〜20公分。<ref name=lei/><ref name=neu/>

== 生態習性 ==
蓮花菰生長在森林及其他的環境裡。<ref name=neu/>常常可以在[[種植園|大型的農場]]裡找到，它寄生在農場的作物上，例如：[[橡膠樹|橡膠樹]]，[[海棗|海棗]]，[[可可樹|可可樹]]。<ref name=jigam>Jigam, A. A., et al. (2012). [http://japsonline.com/admin/php/uploads/340_pdf.pdf Efficacy of ''Thonningia Sanguinea'' Vahl. (Balanophoraceae) root extract against ''Plasmodium berghei'', ''Plasmodium chabaudi'', inflammation and nociception in mice.] {{Wayback|url=http://japsonline.com/admin/php/uploads/340_pdf.pdf |date=20160304035617 }} ''Journal of Applied Pharmaceutical Science'' 2(1) 47–51.</ref>

蓮花菰是一種[[蟲媒花|蟲媒花]]，借由[[蒼蠅|蒼蠅]]和[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]來傳播花粉，這些昆蟲有[[蠅科|蠅科]]和[[麗蠅科|麗蠅科]]的蒼蠅及[[扁琉璃蟻屬|扁琉璃蟻屬]]（''Technomyrmex''）的螞蟻，當它們進入花內[[花蜜|採蜜]]時，同時也為蓮花菰進行了[[授粉|授粉]]。蠅科[[莫蠅屬|莫蠅屬]]（''Morellia''）的蒼蠅會將[[卵|卵]]產在蓮花菰的雄花上，卵孵化成[[幼蟲|幼蟲]]後，幼蟲就以雄花為食物。蓮花菰與莫蠅形成了[[互利共生|互利共生]]的關係，莫蠅幫助蓮花菰授粉，蓮花菰則提供莫蠅產卵的場所，並做為幼蟲的食草為其提供食物。<ref name=goto>{{cite journal |doi=10.1111/j.1442-1984.2011.00338.x|title=A novel brood-site pollination mutualism?: The root holoparasite Thonningia sanguinea (Balanophoraceae) and an inflorescence-feeding fly in the tropical rainforests of West Africa|journal=Plant Species Biology|volume=27|issue=2|pages=164|year=2012|last1=Goto|first1=Ryutaro|last2=Yamakoshi|first2=GEN|last3=Matsuzawa|first3=Tetsuro}}</ref>

== 用途 ==
[[File:Thonningia_MS_3605.jpg|right]]
蓮花菰最廣為人知的用途就是它可以做為[[藥用植物|藥用植物]]，整株植物都可以做藥材，是一種非洲的傳統藥用植物，在許多非洲文化中它被拿來治療很多種疾病。<ref name=neu/>在[[加納|加納]]，用它來防止哮喘發作<ref name=gy>{{cite journal |author=Gyamfi MA, Aniya Y |title=Medicinal herb, Thonningia sanguinea protects against aflatoxin B1 acute hepatotoxicity in Fischer 344 rats |journal=Human & Experimental Toxicology |volume=17 |issue=8 |pages=418–23 |date=August 1998  |pmid=9756133 |url=http://openurl.ingenta.com/content/nlm?genre=article&issn=0960-3271&volume=17&issue=8&spage=418&aulast=Gyamfi |doi=10.1191/096032798678909007}}</ref>和治療[[性傳染疾病|性病]]。<ref name=neu/>在[[象牙海岸|象牙海岸]]和[[剛果民主共和國|剛果]]它被拿來治療[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]。<ref name=oua>Ouattara, K., et al. (2013). [http://scholarsresearchlibrary.com/JMB-vol3-iss2/JMB-2013-3-2-83-87.pdf ''In vitro'' antibacterial activity of ''Thonningia sanguinea'' (Balanophoraceae (Vahl)) flowers extracts.] {{Wayback|url=http://scholarsresearchlibrary.com/JMB-vol3-iss2/JMB-2013-3-2-83-87.pdf |date=20140414145334 }} ''Journal of Microbiology and Biotechnology Research'' 3(2) 83–87.</ref><ref name=ng>N'guessan, J. D., et al. (2007). [http://www.bioline.org.br/pdf?pr07020 Antibacterial activity of the aqueous extract of ''Thonningia sanguinea'' against extended-spectrum-β-lactamases (ESBL) producing ''Escherichia coli'' and ''Klebsiella pneumoniae'' strains.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bioline.org.br/pdf?pr07020 |date=20180722144306 }} ''Tropical Journal of Pharmaceutical Research'' 6(3) 779–83.</ref><ref name=neu/>葉子的煎劑用於治療[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]。和[[辣椒|辣椒]]合用做成外用藥，用來治療[[痔瘡|痔瘡]]和斜頸症（torticollis）。<ref name=neu/>也可治療[[痲瘋病|痲瘋病]]、皮膚感染、[[膿瘡|膿瘡]]、[[齲齒|齲齒]]、[[牙齦病|牙齦病]]、[[發燒|發燒]]、[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]、<ref name=jigam/>[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]、[[佝僂病|佝僂病]]和[[風濕病|風濕病]]。在[[薩伊|薩伊]]，據說可以防止[[尿失禁|尿失禁]]和[[尿床|尿床]]。<ref name=neu/>

在實驗室的研究發現，蓮花菰具有一些藥用功能。它具有[[抗細菌藥|抗菌活性]]，可以抗多種病原體。<ref name=oua/>對於會引起腹瀉，有[[抗藥性|抗藥性]]的[[腸道沙門氏菌|腸道沙門氏菌]]菌株，它具有一些抗菌作用。<ref name=ng2>{{cite journal |author=N'guessan JD, Coulibaly A, Ramanou AA, Okou OC, Djaman AJ, Guédé-Guina F |title=Antibacterial activity of Thonningia sanguinea against some multi-drug resistant strains of Salmonella enterica |journal=African Health Sciences |volume=7 |issue=3 |pages=155–8 |date=September 2007  |pmid=18052869 |pmc=2269722 |doi=10.5555/afhs.2007.7.3.155 |doi_brokendate=2014-04-13 }}</ref>它可能有助於治療經常伴隨著感染[[人類免疫缺陷病毒|人類免疫缺陷病毒]]與[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]出現的[[真菌病|真菌性疾病]]。<ref name=oua2>{{cite journal |author=Ouattara B, Kra AM, Coulibaly A, Guede-Guina F |title=Efficacité de l'extrait éthanolique de Thonningia sanguinea sur Cryptococcus neoformans |trans_title=Efficiency of ethanol of Thonningia sanguinea against Cryptococcus neoformans |language=fr |journal=Santé |volume=17 |issue=4 |pages=219–22 |year=2007 |pmid=18299265 |doi=10.1684/san.2007.0086 |doi_brokendate=2014-04-13 }}</ref>它具有[[抗氧化劑|抗氧化]]活性。<ref name=gy2>{{cite journal |author=Gyamfi MA, Yonamine M, Aniya Y |title=Free-radical scavenging action of medicinal herbs from Ghana: Thonningia sanguinea on experimentally-induced liver injuries |journal=General Pharmacology |volume=32 |issue=6 |pages=661–7 |date=June 1999  |pmid=10401991 |doi=10.1016/S0306-3623(98)00238-9}}</ref>它也許可以保護[[肝臟|肝臟]]，防止[[黃麴毒素|黃麴毒素]]造成肝損傷。<ref name=gy/>對於一些會產生[[β-内酰胺酶|廣效性乙內醯胺酶]]的病原體，例如[[大腸桿菌|大腸桿菌]]及[[克雷伯氏肺炎菌|克雷伯氏肺炎菌]]，在服用抗生素治療這些病菌所產生的疾病時，添加蓮花菰的提取物一起服用，可能有提高治療效果的功效。<ref name=ng/>它有抗[[瘧原蟲屬|瘧原蟲屬]]物種的作用，例如引起[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]的[[惡性瘧原蟲|惡性瘧原蟲]]。<ref name=jigam/>蓮花菰對於[[黑麴黴|黑麴黴]]、[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]（''Candida albicans''）、[[枯草桿菌|枯草桿菌]]、[[綠膿桿菌|綠膿桿菌]]、[[金黃色葡萄球菌|金黃色葡萄球菌]]、宋內志賀氏菌（''Shigella sonnei''）都具有抗菌活性。<ref name=oua3>Ouattara, B., et al. (2008). [http://www.idosi.org/wasj/wasj3%282%29/4.pdf Assessment of antifungal activity of an African medicinal herb ''Thonningia sanguinea'' against ''Cryptococcus neoformans''.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.idosi.org/wasj/wasj3%282%29/4.pdf |date=20150924032916 }} ''World Applied Sciences Journal'' 3(2) 191–94.</ref>

象牙海岸的人民用來獵捕動物的[[箭毒|箭毒]]，其毒藥的成分就含有蓮花菰。<ref name=neu/>它也可以做為[[湯|煮湯]]時的[[調味料|調味料]]。<ref name=sei/>一些地區，它的花序被認為是一種[[春藥|春藥]]。<ref name=neu/>在加納與象牙海岸，會將花序綁在幼兒的腳踝上，激勵他們學習走路，因為花序上的尖刺會阻止他們坐下來。<ref name=burk/>

在某些地方，蓮花菰被認為是一種[[雜草|雜草]]，例如在橡膠園裡面大量生長的蓮花菰就被認為是雜草。<ref name=idu>Idu, M., et al. (2002). [http://www.uniben.edu/abstracts/anatomy-attachment-root-parasite-thonningia-sanguinea-vahl-hevea-brasiliensis Anatomy of attachment of the root parasite ''Thonningia sanguinea'' Vahl. on ''Hevea brasiliensis''.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701193829/http://uniben.edu/abstracts/anatomy-attachment-root-parasite-thonningia-sanguinea-vahl-hevea-brasiliensis |date=2013-07-01 }} ''Indian Journal of Rubber Research'' 15(1) 33–35.</ref>

